headline: Monogram robot marks autonomy milestone; Stereotaxis catheter cleared
summary: Monogram Technologies conducted its first fully autonomous robotic knee replacement surgery, while Stereotaxis won FDA clearance for a robotically navigated electrophysiology mapping catheter.

headline: Analysts Estimate Zimmer Biomet (ZBH) to Report a Decline in Earnings: What to Look Out for
summary: Zimmer (ZBH) doesn't possess the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely earnings beat in its upcoming report. Get prepared with the key expectations.
